      • createBasePropertyDescriptorBuilder

        protected com.foreach.across.modules.entity.config.builders.EntityPropertyDescriptorBuilder createBasePropertyDescriptorBuilder(com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registry.properties.EntityPropertyDescriptor parentDescriptor,
                                                                                                                                String propertyName)
        Utility method to create an initial EntityPropertyDescriptorBuilder. A nested descriptor is made if a parent EntityPropertyDescriptor is given which is not an embedded object or fielset. By default, properties created through this utility method are readable, but not writable.

        If a parent descriptor is an embedded object or fieldset, then the nested properties are not prefixed by their parent property.
        Parameters:
        parentDescriptor - for the new descriptor that should be created
        propertyName - for which a new EntityPropertyDescriptorBuilder should be created
        Returns:
        an EntityPropertyDescriptorBuilder with default configuration.

        Creates a valuefetcher that retrieves the value based on a given property name from the parent descriptor.
        Parameters:
        parentDescriptor - that holds the Map as it s value
        propertyName - key that should be used to retrieve the value from the map
        currentValue - fallback value in case the value can not be fetched via the parent descriptor
